main event: Observers sighted two yellow objects that were traveling in a southerly direction for 1.5 minutes.
interesting points: The objects were described to be smaller than satellites and had landing lights on., No noise was reported during the sighting., The objects disappeared at a 45-degree angle., Observers speculated that the sighting may have been some aircraft., The conclusion of the report indicated probable aircraft as the cause of the sighting.
sighted object: two yellow objects in the sky
witness description: A civilian who reported the sighting.
